  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother was in this military unit, and because he was four years older, he was 19-- between 19 and 20-- or 20-- and he was in this military, or paramilitary unit.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother, my younger brother, my father, and sister were in a so-called Jewish house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In order to prepare deportation, the Jews were first concentrated in Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These Jewish houses were all over the city, and it was difficult to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] know why they started, but they did not start with a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a [INAUDIBLE] transition, and in houses which were not designated Jewish houses, the people had to leave and double up in apartments.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was still fairly comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In our apartment, we had to take in the younger brother of my father and his wife, and a sister of my mother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we still were fairly comfortable in the Jewish house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is how they lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the situation was gradually worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- for example, once they concentrated the Jews in these so-called Jewish houses, they limited their permission to go out of these houses to two or three hours a day, during the day.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, while initially I lived at home and worked in this big factory, in order to continue to work I had to move into the factory, because there was no way that I could commute because of the house.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this episode that the army took me in as a sort of rescue operation came at the end of this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it's an interesting example of how some people were more sympathetic, just to illustrate you this point.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one time, the factory decided to go on strike.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were about 400 workers in the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
